metadata.name: Heiel
metadata.description:
" Heiel, who had bestowed his name on himself hundreds of years ago, in honor of new beginnings and new achievements, was striding down the huge corridors of the Halls of Time while wondering how bored he was and whether it was time to embark on a new adventure or not. Every time his metallic feet made contact with the floor, the sounds reverberated on the walls of the library. "

Heiel is one of the characters of Via-lance.

Visit https://www.via-lance.com/ to learn more about the story and the art behind it.
